documentation.text:
@title KlpManager
 @dev Manages the liquidity for the Kuru liquidity pool.
@dev Throws if called by any account other than the governance address.

@dev Allows the governance address to set the liquidity provider token contract address.
 @param _klp The new liquidity provider token contract address.

@dev Allows the governance address to set the governance address.
 @param _gov The new governance address.

@dev Allows the governance address to set the kuru app lending contract address.
 @param _lendingContractAddress The new kuru app lending contract address.

@dev Allows the governance address to set the external USDC token contract address.
 @param _usdcAddress The new external USDC token contract address.

devdoc.details: Manages the liquidity for the Kuru liquidity pool.

addLiquidity(address,uint256).details: Allows a user to add liquidity to the Kuru liquidity pool.

params._amount: The amount of the asset being added.
params._token: The token address of the asset being added.

returns._0: The amount of liquidity provider tokens minted.

constructor.details: Initializes the contract with the given parameters.

params._klp: The liquidity provider token contract address.
params._lendingContractAddress: The kuru app lending contract address.
params._usdcAddress: The external USDC token contract address.

removeLiquidity(address,uint256).details: Removes liquidity from the pool and returns USDC to the caller.

params._klpAmount: The amount of liquidity tokens to withdraw.
params._tokenOut: The address of the token being withdrawn. Only USDC is supported.

returns._0: The amount of USDC returned to the caller.

setGov(address).details: Allows the governance address to set the governance address.

setKlp(address).details: Allows the governance address to set the liquidity provider token contract address.

params._klp: The new liquidity provider token contract address.

setLendingContractAddress(address).details: Allows the governance address to set the kuru app lending contract address.

params._lendingContractAddress: The new kuru app lending contract address.

setUsdcAddress(address).details: Allows the governance address to set the external USDC token contract address.

params._usdcAddress: The new external USDC token contract address.
